---
const credentials = [
  { label: "NJ License", value: "#P01629" },
  { label: "NJ Fire Safety Certification", value: "#195457" },
];
---

<section class="w-full py-24 px-6 md:px-16" style="background: #fff8f7;">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">

    <!-- Left: content -->
    <div>
      <span class="as-label-caps text-as-primary mb-2 block">ABOUT US</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6" style="color: #291715;">
        Protecting New Jersey &amp; Pennsylvania Since 1977
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: #5d3f3b;">
        Alert Sprinkler was established in 1977 and incorporated in 1978. For over 45 years we have been
        the trusted name in fire sprinkler protection across New Jersey and southeastern Pennsylvania.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-10" style="color: #5d3f3b;">
        Our scope covers the full lifecycle — engineering, design, installation, and reinforcement of
        fire sprinkler systems, as well as inspections, testing, repairs, and ongoing maintenance.
        We are fully insured and licensed by the State of New Jersey.
      </p>

      <!-- License / certification pills -->
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-10">
        {credentials.map((c) => (
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-as-primary shrink-0">—</span>
            <span class="text-sm" style="color: #291715;">
              <span class="font-bold">{c.label}:</span> {c.value}
            </span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>

      <a href="/alert-sprinkler/about" class="as-btn-primary inline-block text-base px-8 py-4">
        Learn More About Us
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: 2×2 image grid + stat callout -->
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Logo overlay top-right -->
      <img
        src="/alert-sprinkler/alert-logo.png"
        alt=""
        aria-hidden="true"
        class="hidden lg:block absolute -top-16 -right-12 z-10 w-44 pointer-events-none"
      />

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
        <div class="overflow-hidden border border-as-border" style="border-radius: 0.25rem; aspect-ratio: 1;">
          <img
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAaBsZ8KP8agvAtmGrY0n20wVEZ77rC_1jL6iY3FgIesxT97sirkIgflr420yT8DWbSIadTcUniCqhyu0YUq8RlgFfKLP3DBlR5iDQUvGgiMoyQ5Oe1LXJtEmNF5duKhN2Wdd48EU8UMPGewrwtMsbOeeo4MgpO-kxYNY_M3WR_sSEFfVaBJhxJG6D9nyVsD3c5_nSzwmABwLccO05NvPOs0ibqmy3zkIXMgX1hHEaHe5se87BglB4-8D7C1i4EwyR2GUSPGgoTNpM"
            alt="Fire protection engineer inspecting system"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden border border-as-border" style="border-radius: 0.25rem; aspect-ratio: 1;">
          <img
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAvHM3RTVyeq5o4x7hCtXOW2Qd21YYy9ckx_KtZ6qgtCVyUNu8ahxLkvWAbWn_j7J7xoKwxcvwQeNjqu74i52DvQpaKhEz2Kh2bQ3bXNRgRMCWfYxCN5dIXEi7m2XYELdMM75GYy3pVVgewdNwQoGKjr6Lmj9KLjO1ufVp6GxZjEW7Alzjbjusi1p6Tpn443uO8WqbxghO68nhRyotXtwn1LTXgwGQhjXf83BZfxH0qYgLfrFTe8dnQw0mZ6BSP-XuK9TMrdWJXotgc"
            alt="Industrial sprinkler system"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden border border-as-border" style="border-radius: 0.25rem; aspect-ratio: 1;">
          <img
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAFTX0cXlnrmEyisjDamWzXIew50WtE-jvYXqIUTTU_UwrzBMxywMjFkZKyNfDZD4O43avqhQBYVm9tD3etd7SpY5_qj3tYwsyr9ShJmvztbhXV4t2ahySKD8FHR0CX8rYmLT4T3ntvEDsOHM7OF4ugJwI7shBozQoQnEKkyGzne8L0jTnMVXLqzhvpezlpEZMUq5GyHIQdPY1hL3Po4865hqa3Z_jDoAEc5w4hOShG76L6wEEeVb-sHdiqDZGzevv2E1xeqC2LZLE"
            alt="Institutional fire protection"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="overflow-hidden border border-as-border" style="border-radius: 0.25rem; aspect-ratio: 1;">
          <img
            src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCjoQL1GazQFZL3TR9IZ8OL3VnJlNuWMLbxm9aYARE1PuEbHmAaT96LV7X2m-kQhBVxUvf0ZihnsiG65shfn6sWoOSuK2QRndTtJncD-HgplBGzT9YydsdkAUgZXjrDV7Qnpvcc-59CdIgeSiVQilwqTSiZnw3ngqoxtOms0kC9LscPA610Ix9gCmHbJ6SYddns_gxAucrOT9Mp6FxYZJ8DRYui7Fw1HnLlrUorl1lApfZTe0wYxWPf-hXkiOKhDFuTKd3mCS0tuI0"
            alt="Residential fire sprinkler system"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Floating stat card -->
      <div
        class="absolute -bottom-8 -left-8 bg-white p-8 border border-as-border shadow-sm max-w-60"
        style="border-radius: 0.25rem;"
      >
        <span class="font-extrabold block mb-1 text-as-primary" style="font-size: 56px; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">45+</span>
        <span class="as-label-caps" style="color: #5d3f3b;">Years of Continuous NJ Safety Service</span>
